# EP_COOKIE format note

EP_COOKIE should include your vBulletin session cookie. If Elitepvpers shows a Cloudflare "Verify You're Human" page, the MCP will auto-solve it via Byparr (requires Docker).

For faster EPVP access without Docker:
1. Visit https://www.elitepvpers.com/forum/ in a browser
2. Complete Cloudflare challenge if shown
3. Export ALL cookies including `cf_clearance` (browser devtools > Application > Cookies)
4. Add to EP_COOKIE: `bbsessionhash=...; cf_clearance=...`

UnknownCheats doesn't use Cloudflare - regular session cookies work directly.